These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, jazz, blues, punk
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
3. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Music-Genre        | metal | jazz   | punk | blues    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, skiing, sailing, snowboarding
There are 4 different nationalities: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the french is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. the french is the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
6. the french is the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Sport   | sailing | surfing  | skiing  | snowboarding |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, firefighter, librarian, writer
1. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the writer##3
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. the writer is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
4. the writer is on the right of the librarian##1
5. the nurse is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| Job   | librarian        | writer     | nurse | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, horse, guinea-pig, hamster
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. the owner of the horse is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Pet         | hamster | bird | horse | guinea-pig |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, engineer, police-officer, lawyer
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the engineer is the fan of punk##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
6. the photographer is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Job   | photographer | lawyer | police-officer | engineer |

