.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, epic, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, tennis, skiing, cycling
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| Sport   | cycling | tennis     | sailing  | skiing  |

