.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, mystery, western
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit, snake, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| Pet     | chinchilla | snake  | lizard     | rabbit |

