.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, pilot, project-manager, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, action, adventure, musical
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the pilot##3
2. the teacher is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the teacher##3
4. the teacher is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the coach is between the teacher and the pilot##2
6. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
7. the person watching action movies is between the coach and the person watching adventure movies##2
8. the coach is on the left or right of the pilot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | pilot | coach      | teacher | project-manager |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | musical | action    | adventure            |

