.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
4 different games are played: domino, chess, snooker, mah-jongg
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, mouse, turtle
1. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
2. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing chess##1
3. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hamster and the person playing snooker##2
4. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
5. the person playing snooker is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | chess   | domino | snooker |
| Pet    | turtle     | hamster | cat     | mouse  |

