.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
There are 4 different nationalities: french, russian, italian, indonesian
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the indonesian##1
2. the french is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the indonesian is between the french and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the indonesian is on the left or right of the french##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the russian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Nationality   | italian | russian | indonesian        | french    |

