.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, carrot, cherry, lemon
House: cape-cod, colonial, victorian, tower
1. the victorian house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
2. the victorian house is in an even position##4
3. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
4. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cherry is between the colonial house and the victorian house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | lemon | carrot  | cherry  | cabbage |
| House   | tower  | victorian | cape-cod | colonial   |

