2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
4. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
