.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk, lemonade, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person drinking sprite is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person drinking soy-milk##2
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk         | sprite   | lemonade |
| Sport   | soccer    | skateboarding | weightlifting | ice-hockey   |

