.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, peach, apricot, spinach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person eating apricot##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person eating artichoke##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person eating spinach##1
4. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
5. the person eating artichoke is in an even position##4
6. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Food   | peach | artichoke | apricot    | spinach |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

