.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, goat, rat, horse
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, nigerian, turkish
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4
3. the japanese is the owner of the rat##1
4. the nigerian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the japanese is between the turkish and the nigerian##2
6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Pet         | horse   | rat | fish | goat    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | japanese  | turkish     | american |

