2. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the modern house##3
3. the modern house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
4. the tower house is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the american is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
6. the modern house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indonesian | american  | pakistani |
| House     | modern      | cape-cod       | tower | colonial     |

